Hey! You made it!!! Sorry for making you wait so long. I wanted to make it an experience. Never do I know exactly what I should do for this. I can't really just get you honmei choco, some flowers, some ramen, and call it a day. So, while this takes a TON of effort and it's not prefect, it's what I came up with just for you. Enough about the site. 
<br><br>
百合は本当に大切な存在です。初めて出会ったあの日から、自分の人生を変えてくれました。思いがけず私の前に現れて、今まで欠けていると気づかなかった幸せを教えてくれました。一緒にいることで、想像もしていなかったことや、できるなんて思ってもみなかったことをたくさん経験してきました。
<br><br>
百合のような人がそばにいてくれることにどれだけ感謝しているか、言葉では言い尽くせません。何気ない日常でさえ、一緒だと特別に感じられるし、ここにいてくれると思うだけで心が落ち着きます。
<br><br>
そばにいてくれて、自分を選んでくれて、そして世界で一番幸せな人にしてくれてありがとう。百合を愛せて、愛してもらえて本当に幸せです。
<br><br>
Happy Valentine's, Beautiful.
<br><br>
(People have warned me how cringey ^this^ might sound, so here's the original English version to it.)
<br>
Yuri, you mean so much to me. You've changed my life. You came into my life unexpectedly and brought me a kind of joy I didn't know I was missing. With you, I've experienced things I never imagined or believed to be possible. 
<br><br>
I don’t think I can fully put into words how grateful I am to have someone like you in my life. You make even the ordinary moments feel special, and somehow just knowing you’re there brings me comfort. 
<br><br>
Thank you for being here for me, for choosing me, and making me the happiest person alive. I am truly lucky to love you and to be loved by you. Happy Valentine's, Beautiful. 
